description:
“For it by grace you have been saved, though faith, and this is not from yourselves, it is the gift of God–not by works, so that no one can boast. For we are God’s handiwork, created in Christ Jesus to do good works which God prepared in advance for us to do.” - Ephesians 2:8-10
